{"tid":717511,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"女偶像小褲褲卡股溝　露屁股蛋被網友撻伐","createTime":"2018-06-26T05:42:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-28T02:10:08.000Z","uid":147522,"like":9,"dislike":163,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"898371ebfaaf149e62eb75b0004fb508ad2abb45","tid":717511,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T05:42:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/26/134212_9939137b4dc11c4237981a90d799a2d8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F26%2F134212_9939137b4dc11c4237981a90d799a2d8.png&h=f22ed497&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本偶像團體SKE48成員熊崎晴香，日前在一場演唱會上，親民的下台與粉絲互動，沒想到被粉絲拍到露底褲畫面，內褲還卡在股溝之間，兩顆屁股蛋就這樣露出，影片一出引發熱烈討論<br />\n<br />\n熊崎晴香在一場演唱會上，為展現親民的風格，下台與粉絲互動，沒想到粉絲拿起手機錄影這一刻，竟意外拍到熊崎晴香露底褲，內褲還夾在股溝，兩顆屁股蛋形狀就這樣露出，這名粉絲還PO上網路，被網友撻伐。<br />\n<br />\n影片一出引發熱烈討論，拍攝者被網友斥責，但有另一派網友持相反意見，認為熊崎晴香是故意的，明知道角度關係還硬要蹲下來，「這屁股髒死了，還什麼國民偶像」、「一直蹲是怕人家拍不到嗎。」"},{"pid":"d32a31d1227f31eb08aff543099d0669e4b705b3","tid":717511,"uid":32380,"like":417,"dislike":2,"score":415,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T05:43:01.000Z","msg":"你有一分鐘"},{"pid":"74f0cc33681dace3d6d812893676cee8471ea8be","tid":717511,"uid":122264,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T05:43:52.000Z","msg":"屌"},{"pid":"8e40f208920c6d3e65f3abe21bc3db6d9556fc79","tid":717511,"uid":35930,"like":285,"dislike":4,"score":281,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T05:44:57.000Z","msg":"D格仲厚過av"},{"pid":"650744617ff04f763d51ce82a34b56c801e81b03","tid":717511,"uid":7673,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T05:46:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c739036e9ea879c003cb8145c8d626c81b648be4","tid":717511,"uid":29620,"like":113,"dislike":2,"score":111,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T05:46:57.000Z","msg":"咁撚樣不如唔好PO圖啦"},{"pid":"b98e1a42eefb004ab82c5d37cca1c3079dd98e89","tid":717511,"uid":146917,"like":17,"dis